entry.summary:

Stanadyne Fuel Manager Complete "Top Load" Assembly For GM 6.5L diesel engine with 5 micron element, 12V water sensor & 100 watt heater

All Fuel Manager units remove both particulates and water, and can be adapted for a variety of applications. Optional modular features can be added by the manufacturer, dealer, and in most cases the user.

Each employ Stanadyne's unique filtration process, trapping more impurities and water without impeding the flow rate. The product's design permits the replacement of elements without the use of tools and without spilling fuel, making service easy in the shop or in the field. When an element is replaced, an easily opened drain valve allows the filter to be completely and neatly emptied before it is removed.

entry.title: Fuel Additive Sampler Pack
entry.summary:
Vendor: Stanadyne
Type: Additive
Price: 60.00

New to Diesel Fuel Additives and not sure which one to buy? Or just want to try out the industry-leading offerings? Here's your chance! Diesel Parts Canada is happy to have a Fuel Additive Sample Pack available, where you get one of each of the following products:

One 16 oz bottle of Alliant Power ULTRAGUARD Diesel Fuel Treatment
All-season, multi-functional fuel treatment that provides complete fuel system and injector protection for all diesel engines.

One 16 oz bottle of Alliant Power LUBRIGUARD Diesel Fuel Treatement
Highly concentrated lubricating fuel treatment with cetane improver that provides superior fuel system protection for all diesel engines.

One 16 oz bottle of Alliant Power WINTERGUARD Diesel Fuel Treatment
﻿Cold weather fuel treatment designed to prevent common diesel fuel issues relating to extreme cold temperatures.

One 8 oz bottle of Stanadyne Performance Formula All Season Diesel Fuel Additive
The premium all-season, multi-function diesel fuel additive, designed to tackle virtually any diesel fuel related problem.

One 8 oz bottle of Stanadyne Performance Formula Warm Weather Blend Diesel Fuel Additive
Formulated to provide the same benefits as Performance. Formula All Season Protection (Blue Label) except without cold weather protection. Performance Formula Warm Weather Blend is recommended when ambient temperatures are above 40°F (4° C).

One 8 oz bottle of Stanadyne Performance Formula Injector Cleaner Diesel Fuel Additive
Stanadyne Performance Formula Injector Cleaner is formulated to prevent and eliminate Internal Diesel Injector Deposits (IDID) commonly found in Common Rail and other type of Injectors. These deposits affect injector performance, which results in various engine related issues.

One 8 oz bottle of Stanadyne Lubricity Formula Diesel Fuel Additive
Extra strength lubricity formula to protect fuel systems against the effect of untreated diesel fuel.

One 8 oz bottle of Stanadyne Gasoline Fuel Additive
Stanadyne Gasoline Additive is designed to protect Gasoline Direct Injection and traditional gas fuel systems, while restoring engine performance. This unique formula helps eliminate deposits that form on critical fuel system and engine components to keep those components clean, lubricated, and maintenance free.

LUBRIGUARD™ has been developed using a unique combination of additives designed to supplement dry fuels that are known to cause premature wear of the fuel system. This diesel fuel treatment is available in three different sizes listed in the table below. Lubricates Fuel System Reducing Friction & Wear Restores Engine Power & Torque Improves Fuel Economy Increases Cetane for Improved Engine Combustion Cleans Internal & External Injector Deposits Stabilizes & Extends Fuel Shelf Life Removes Water by Demulsification Protects Against Fuel System Rust & Corrosion Alliant Power LUBRIGUARD™ has been formulated using technologically advanced chemistry designed to protect the most advanced high-pressure common rail diesel fuel systems as well as conventional fuel systems.
